Approve Users

Resolve Issues

Broadcast Notification

Suspend Account

2. User Management

Full control over all users

View Users

Filter by:

Role (Student / Tutor / Counselor)

Department

Status (Active / Pending / Suspended)

Rating (Tutors/Counselors)

