Reset user password (force reset)

Edit limited profile fields (admin override)

View full activity history

3. Session Management (Global Control)

Admin sees ALL sessions

Displays:

Student name

Tutor/Counselor name

Date & time

Mode (online / in-person)

Status (Upcoming / Completed / Cancelled / No-show)

Reason/request message

Actions:

Cancel session (with reason)

Force reschedule

Mark as completed (admin override)

Flag suspicious activity

View session history per user

Smart Flags:

Repeated cancellations

Frequent no-shows

Overbooking attempts

4. Booking Requests Oversight

